# ============ POST-DEPLOY ORCHESTRATION ============
# UCC-1 filing metadata used by post-deploy-orchestrate.cjs.
# UCC1_FILING_HASH is the Pinata CID of the filed UCC-1 document (already set above).
# UCC1_FILING_NUMBER is the official filing number assigned by the New Mexico SOS.
# GitHub variable: UCC1_FILING_NUMBER (or set as a secret if deemed sensitive)
UCC1_FILING_NUMBER="20260000078753"
UCC1_JURISDICTION="New Mexico Secretary of State"


